{"tid":2513244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度男入境中国解除隔離後檢出陽性　期間到訪多個城市","createTime":"2021-05-02T10:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T12:25:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":285,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab4c5f67c2a32cd2e1e7101b94c366b376f8270","tid":2513244,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:54:13.000Z","msg":"內地高度防範新冠肺炎輸入疫情。日前，一名印度籍男子入境中國後，在隔離期間多次檢測為陰性。在解除隔離後，他從上海乘坐列車浙江杭州，再轉乘列車抵達義烏，最終在義烏被檢出陽性結果，被列為新增無症狀感染者。<br />\n<br />\n浙江金華市周日（2日）通報，5月1日無新增新冠肺炎確診病例，新增一名無症狀感染者（義烏市1宗、為境外輸入），即為上述印度籍男子。2021年1月1日0時至5月1日24時，尚在醫學觀察無症狀感染者1宗（義烏市1宗）。<br />\n<br />\n通報指，該名感染者2021年4月14日從非洲尼日爾乘坐AF339航班抵達巴黎，4月15日從巴黎搭乘AF198航班至上海入境，隨即在上海某集中隔離點隔離3日，4月19日從上海專車轉運至嘉善縣某隔離場所進行醫學觀察，期間多次核酸檢測均為陰性。<br />\n<br />\n4月30日，該男子解除隔離後，乘坐K759次列車至杭州南站，後轉乘T101次列車到達義烏站。抵達義烏後，直接點對點轉運至綜合服務點繼續集中隔離醫學觀察。5月1日核酸檢測結果為陽性，無發熱、咳嗽等症狀，經專家組診斷為新冠肺炎無症狀感染者。<br />\n<br />\n目前，該感染者已在定點醫院隔離醫學觀察，已排查密切接觸者均已按要求落實管控措施，涉及場所均落實了有效消毒。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01 .com/即時中國/ 619921</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b1eaa9aa184b9c97836d791185ad527807a9467f","tid":2513244,"uid":130079,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"武漢新德里上海浙江杭州肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7d6dedb98f94483c957fec8ad01868b9de076a","tid":2513244,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a18b919e4f045db4334cd8bef3e7d3b7b5beb79","tid":2513244,"uid":16057,"like":146,"dislike":0,"score":146,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"物歸原主"},{"pid":"46a67c1608630c18adab195dde36bffa0f6be4eb","tid":2513244,"uid":126731,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebd779113aa754ef12c8d3ceca95848140b5b58","tid":2513244,"uid":3457,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:57:06.000Z","msg":"回家了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5287aa87fa1b87f949ca28cdc0ce69f4d32b0dcd","tid":2513244,"uid":293943,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"咁都計外來輸入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50aa3b68fce1a68a21eff4d4cf2dfd52e89029a5","tid":2513244,"uid":273791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:58:21.000Z","msg":"愛回家"},{"pid":"da67ba005d3b5adad71e8264080ee19a6f03fb52","tid":2513244,"uid":3873,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢啲.jpg"},{"pid":"14761d545ab8b1136696c4e36adcab6c785c9e40","tid":2513244,"uid":388418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f83df38ca7ff836a0a303df08f6e99cc40b15a","tid":2513244,"uid":27946,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"兩大人口大國減咁d對世界都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6129dd8f2fe8ebe67e256403dbc940b51fc22a","tid":2513244,"uid":194597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:02:12.000Z","msg":"其實武肺進化到識避過檢測期都唔出奇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a02053c9861e8255952d5bf6187cb2f015ec77b","tid":2513244,"uid":11291,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36